org.miloss.fgsms.services.interfaces.policyconfiguration

Class ServicePolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.miloss.fgsms.services.interfaces.policyconfiguration.ServicePolicy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MachinePolicy, ProcessPolicy, StatisticalServicePolicy, StatusServicePolicy, TransactionalWebServicePolicy

    public class ServicePolicy
extends Object
implements Serializable
    ServicePolicy - The service policy is one of the most important elements in fgsms, it defines how agents react to observed traffic keyed on URLs
